	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvus et incolumis ad meos sum reversus; inveni ipsos quoque salvos per domini gratiam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vobis omnibus pro humanitate ac benficentia vestra magnas habeo gratias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam te quoque hic aliquando conspicere et ea tibi, quę in me perpetuo confers beneficia, referre queam.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Octiduo postquam redii, uxor mea septima me nunc prole donavit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alias nihil est, quod nunc scribam; silent enim mirifice omnia, neque quicquam fertur novi, nisi quod quidam nescio quid de pacificatione inter Caesarem et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8112">Gallum</persName> quadam mussitant.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae si procedat, una cum <persName type="citizen_name">regno Angliae</persName> ecclesiae quoque nostrae periclitabuntur.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus adsit nobis sua gratia et dissipet consilia malignantium.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Amen.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvi sint tui omnes una cum fratribus nostris charissimis.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Nostri omnes te salutant.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l167" cert="high">Genevę</placeName> a quibusdam contraverti audio, an excommunicatorum infantes baptizari debeant necne; sic semper novi aliquid ex illa <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2549" cert="high">Africa</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 6. iunii 1554.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Has literas mittes iis, ad quos pertinent, oro.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[oannes] Hallerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae pastori fidelissimo, domino ac compatri suo plurimum colendo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">M. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrych Bullingern</persName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
